<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<title>错误页面</title>
	<style type="text/css">
		.error404_wrap{
			text-align: center;
		}
		.error404_wrap figure{
			width: 4.75rem;
			height: 4.15rem;
			background-image: url(/images/common/shibai.png);
			-webkit-background-size: cover;
		    -moz-background-size: cover;
		    -ms-background-size: cover;
		    -o-background-size: cover;
		    background-size: cover;
		    margin: 7.0rem auto 1.0rem;
		}
		.error404_wrap .error404_refresh{
			width: 5.0rem;
			height: 1.5rem;
			line-height: 1.5rem;
			margin: 3.0rem auto 0;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="error404_wrap clearfix">
		<figure></figure>
		<h2>哎呀...您访问的页面找不到了，请先歇一会儿</h2>
		<div class="tac bdc_cb bdr_4 error404_refresh">重新查看页面</div>
	</div>
	<script type="text/javascript">
		$(function(){
			$(".error404_refresh").click(function() {
		    	window.location.reload();
			});
		});
	</script>
</body>
</html>